{
  "id": "api/core/PlatformRef",
  "title": "PlatformRef",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L166-L304\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L166-L304\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/PlatformRef\", \"name\": \"PlatformRef\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"platformref\">PlatformRef<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#platformref\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>The Angular platform is the entry point for Angular on a web page. Each page\nhas exactly one platform, and services (such as reflection) which are common\nto every Angular application running on the page are bound in its scope.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/PlatformRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformRef</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#injector\"><span class=\"member-name\">injector</span>: Injector</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#destroyed\"><span class=\"member-name\">destroyed</span></a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#bootstrapModuleFactory\"><span class=\"member-name\">bootstrapModuleFactory</span>&#x3C;M>(moduleFactory: NgModuleFactory&#x3C;M>, options?: BootstrapOptions): Promise&#x3C;NgModuleRef&#x3C;M>></a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#bootstrapModule\"><span class=\"member-name\">bootstrapModule</span>&#x3C;M>(moduleType: Type&#x3C;M>, compilerOptions: (CompilerOptions &#x26; BootstrapOptions) | Array&#x3C;CompilerOptions &#x26; BootstrapOptions> = []): Promise&#x3C;NgModuleRef&#x3C;M>></a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#onDestroy\"><span class=\"member-name\">onDestroy</span>(callback: () => void): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#destroy\"><span class=\"member-name\">destroy</span>()</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>A page's platform is initialized implicitly when a platform is created via a platform factory\n(e.g. <a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\"><code>platformBrowser</code></a>), or explicitly by calling the <a href=\"api/core/createPlatform\"><code>createPlatform</code></a> function.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Property</th>\n        <th>Description</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"injector\"></a>\n          <code><span class=\"member-name\">injector</span>: <a href=\"api/core/Injector\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injector</a></code>\n        </td>\n        <td><span class=\"read-only-property\">Read-only.</span>\n          <p>Retrieve the platform <a href=\"api/core/Injector\"><code>Injector</code></a>, which is the parent injector for\nevery Angular application on the page and provides singleton providers.</p>\n\n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"destroyed\"></a>\n          <code><span class=\"member-name\">destroyed</span></code>\n        </td>\n        <td><span class=\"read-only-property\">Read-only.</span>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"bootstrapModuleFactory\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"bootstrapmodulefactory\">\n        bootstrapModuleFactory()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#bootstrapmodulefactory\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L185-L240\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L185-L240\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Creates an instance of an <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> for the given platform\nfor offline compilation.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">bootstrapModuleFactory</span>&#x3C;M>(moduleFactory: <a href=\"api/core/NgModuleFactory\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleFactory</a>&#x3C;M>, options?: BootstrapOptions): Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/NgModuleRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleRef</a>&#x3C;M>></code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>moduleFactory</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/NgModuleFactory\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleFactory</a><m></m></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>options</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code>BootstrapOptions</code>.</p>\n      <p>Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/NgModuleRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleRef</a>&#x3C;M>></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"simple-example\">Simple Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#simple-example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nmy_module.ts:\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  <a href=\"api/core/NgModule#imports\" class=\"code-anchor\">imports</a>: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a>]\n})\nclass MyModule {}\n\nmain.ts:\nimport {MyModuleNgFactory} from './my_module.ngfactory';\nimport {<a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>} from '@angular/platform-browser';\n\nlet moduleRef = <a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>().bootstrapModuleFactory(MyModuleNgFactory);\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"bootstrapModule\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"bootstrapmodule\">\n        bootstrapModule()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#bootstrapmodule\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L241-L264\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L241-L264\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Creates an instance of an <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> for a given platform using the given runtime compiler.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">bootstrapModule</span>&#x3C;M>(<a href=\"api/core/NgModuleFactory#moduleType\" class=\"code-anchor\">moduleType</a>: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;M>, compilerOptions: (<a href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">CompilerOptions</a> &#x26; BootstrapOptions) | Array&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">CompilerOptions</a> &#x26; BootstrapOptions> = []): Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/NgModuleRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleRef</a>&#x3C;M>></code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>moduleType</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a><m></m></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>compilerOptions</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code>(<a href=\"api/core/CompilerOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">CompilerOptions</a> &#x26; BootstrapOptions) | Array<compileroptions &#x26;=\"\" bootstrapoptions=\"\"></compileroptions></code>.</p>\n      <p>Optional. Default is <code>[]</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns-1\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/NgModuleRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModuleRef</a>&#x3C;M>></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <tr>\n      <td class=\"usage-notes\">\n        <h4 id=\"simple-example-1\">Simple Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#simple-example-1\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h4>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  <a href=\"api/core/NgModule#imports\" class=\"code-anchor\">imports</a>: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a>]\n})\nclass MyModule {}\n\nlet moduleRef = <a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>().bootstrapModule(MyModule);\n</code-example>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"onDestroy\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ondestroy\">\n        onDestroy()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#ondestroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L279-L283\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L279-L283\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Register a listener to be called when the platform is disposed.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">onDestroy</span>(callback: () => void): void</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-2\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>callback</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p>Type: <code>() => void</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns-2\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"destroy\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"destroy\">\n        destroy()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/PlatformRef#destroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L290-L301\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L290-L301\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Destroy the Angular platform and all Angular applications on the page.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"><span class=\"member-name\">destroy</span>()</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-3\">Parameters</h4>\n<p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/assertPlatform\n - api/core/createPlatform\n - api/core/createPlatformFactory\n - api/core/getPlatform\n - api/core/platformCore\n - api/core/testing/TestBed\n - api/core/testing/TestBedStatic\n - api/platform-browser-dynamic/platformBrowserDynamic\n - api/platform-browser-dynamic/testing/platformBrowserDynamicTesting\n - api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\n - api/platform-browser/testing/platformBrowserTesting\n - api/platform-server/platformDynamicServer\n - api/platform-server/platformServer\n - api/platform-server/testing/platformServerTesting\n - api/platform-webworker-dynamic/platformWorkerAppDynamic\n - api/platform-webworker/bootstrapWorkerUi\n - api/platform-webworker/platformWorkerApp\n - api/platform-webworker/platformWorkerUi\n - api/upgrade/static/downgradeModule\n - guide/npm-packages\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade-performance\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CompilerOptions\n - api/core/Injector\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/NgModule#imports\n - api/core/NgModuleFactory\n - a